            "text": [
              "<p>Each point on the homework counts for 50% of the grade.</p>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "VyDbf0t-IyUl74hx",
          "title": "Text 22",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>Each point on the test counts for 4% of the grade. </p>"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      {
        "id": "x__93Dhe89dg53tk",
        "title": "Text 23",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>If Baruti gets every point except, for example, point 2, his homework percentage is 50%, and his test percentage is 96%.</p>"
          ]
        }
